     `line_type' y `color'.

     Ejemplo:

          (%i1) load(draw)$
          (%i2) draw2d(fill_color  = red,
                       line_width  = 6,
                       line_type   = dots,
                       transparent = false,
                       fill_color  = blue,
                       rectangle([-2,-2],[8,-1]), /* opposite vertices */
                       transparent = true,
                       line_type   = solid,
                       line_width  = 1,
                       rectangle([9,4],[2,-1.5]),
                       xrange      = [-3,10],
                       yrange      = [-3,4.5] )$

